<! [CDATA[
 SHEIN Logo
Shein is a Chinese online fashion and sports retailer founded in 2008 by Chris Xu in Guangzhou, China. It currently serves over 220 countries. The company is known for its cheaply priced apparel which is made directly in China. The company intentionally stays out of the media and goes through great lengths to hide its origins. The “About Us” on its US web site has no mention of its Chinese origins nor its executive team.
You can download theSheinlogo on full-version of the page.
